@startuml Spotify-Visualizer-DataFlow

!define USER_COLOR #FFD700
!define SPOTIFY_COLOR #1DB954
!define FRONTEND_COLOR #FFE0B2
!define BACKEND_COLOR #C8E6C9

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontColor #333333
skinparam sequenceLifelineBackgroundColor #E1F5FE

title Spotify Visualizer - Authentication & Data Flow

actor User
participant "Browser\n(React Frontend)" as Frontend <<FRONTEND_COLOR>>
participant "Flask Backend\nAPI" as Backend <<BACKEND_COLOR>>
participant "Spotify OAuth\nServer" as Spotify <<SPOTIFY_COLOR>>

== Authentication Flow ==

User -> Frontend: Clicks "Login with Spotify"
Frontend -> Backend: GET /login
Backend -> Spotify: Redirect to OAuth consent screen
Spotify -> User: Shows login & permission page
User -> Spotify: Approves access
Spotify -> Backend: Redirect to /callback with auth code
Backend -> Spotify: Exchange code for access token
Spotify -> Backend: Returns access token
Backend -> Frontend: Redirect with token in URL\n(http://localhost:5173?token=...)
Frontend -> Frontend: Extracts token from URL\nStores in state

== Data Fetching Flow ==

Frontend -> Frontend: User selects tab\n(Recent/Top Tracks/Top Artists)
Frontend -> Backend: GET /recent\nHeaders: Authorization: Bearer {token}
Backend -> Spotify: Use token to fetch user's recently played
Spotify -> Backend: Returns track data
Backend -> Frontend: JSON response with tracks
Frontend -> Frontend: Renders tracks in UI

== Component Hierarchy ==

App.jsx: Main component\n- Manages token state\n- Handles authentication\n- Manages active tab
├── Header: Displays user info
├── Tabs: Navigation between views
└── Page Component (selected):
    ├── RecentlyPlayed.jsx
    │   └── TrackList: Displays tracks
    ├── TopTracks.jsx
    │   ├── PeriodPills: Period selector\n    │   └── TrackList: Displays tracks
    └── TopArtists.jsx
        ├── PeriodPills: Period selector
        └── ArtistList: Displays artists

== Backend API Endpoints ==

GET /login
  └─> Initiates OAuth flow

GET /callback?code=...
  └─> Handles OAuth callback

GET /user
  Header: Authorization: Bearer {token}
  └─> Returns user profile data

GET /recent
  Header: Authorization: Bearer {token}
  └─> Returns recently played tracks

GET /top/tracks/<period>
  Header: Authorization: Bearer {token}
  Periods: week, month, 6months, year
  └─> Returns top tracks for period

GET /top/artists/<period>
  Header: Authorization: Bearer {token}
  Periods: week, month, 6months, year
  └─> Returns top artists for period

@enduml
